			<h5>6.1.1. The Kaltura Properties may include, without limitation:</h5><br />
				<p class="indent">6.1.1.1. Articles and documentation for use in connection with the use and implementation of our APIs (collectively, "Documentation");</p>
				<p class="indent">6.1.1.2. Textual materials, such as textual product information made available through Kaltura Associates Web Service ("Text Materials"); and</p>
				<p class="indent">6.1.1.2. Other forms of digital content, data, text, images, logos, user interface designs and other creative designs, audio and video (with the Text Materials, collectively, "AWS Content").</p>
			<h5>6.1.2. Except as may be expressly authorized under this Agreement:</h5>
			<p>You may edit Text Materials only by deleting text from and reducing the length of the Text Materials and only if, in doing so, you do not materially alter the meaning of the Text Materials or cause the Text Materials to become factually incorrect or misleading.</p>
